videos.description: Delvon Randall gets his third interception of the season and lets people know how to follow him.
videos.headline: Randall makes a pick, sends a message to UConn

videos.description: David Hood barrels up the middle which leads to a 1-yard touchdown on the next play.
videos.headline: Hood's 11-yard run leads to TD on next play

videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs finds Quayvon Skanes from six yards out for the touchdown to tie the game 7-7.
videos.headline: Skanes ties it up for the Huskies

videos.description: Brodrick Yancy's costly fumble is recovered by Marshe Terry and sets up a short touchdown for UConn.
videos.headline: Yancy fumble sets up UConn TD

videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs finds Arkeel Newsome as UConn extends their lead over Temple.
videos.headline: Newsome fights to get in end zone

videos.description: Tyler Coyle reads the pass from Logan Marchi and takes it back for a 34-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Coyle takes pick to the house for UConn

videos.description: Temple responds with a 9-yard touchdown from Logan Marchi to Isaiah Wright.
videos.headline: Marchi finds Wright for wide open TD

videos.description: Ryquell Armstead finds the end zone from 10 yards out to make it 28-21.
videos.headline: Armstead makes it a one score game
